flowchart TD
    GPS[1957-1972<br/>General Problem Solver<br/>symbolic heuristic search]
    MCTS[2006-2016<br/>MCTS and AlphaGo<br/>value-guided tree search]
    CoT[2022<br/>Chain-of-Thought<br/>single reasoning path]
    SC[2022<br/>Self-Consistency<br/>sample many final paths]
    ReAct[2022<br/>ReAct<br/>reasoning plus actions]
    ToT[2023<br/>Tree of Thoughts<br/>LLM proposes and evaluates search states]
    GoT[2023-2024<br/>Graph / Algorithm of Thoughts<br/>non-tree reasoning graphs]
    LATS[2023-2024<br/>Language Agent Tree Search<br/>planning for agents]
    TTC[2024-2025<br/>test-time compute<br/>o1 / R1 style long reasoning]
    Misread[Common misread<br/>prompt trick rather than search interface]

    GPS --> MCTS
    GPS --> ToT
    MCTS --> ToT
    CoT --> SC
    CoT --> ToT
    SC --> ToT
    ReAct --> ToT
    ToT --> GoT
    ToT --> LATS
    ToT --> TTC
    ToT -.-> Misread
